<br>
I start many of new chars in the Qeynos area when a new server opens. One thing I have seen on Luclin, Lanys and Torv is that Pyzjin spawns alot more than it appears to on the more 'established' servers.<br>
<br>
That is probably a result of several things...newbies all over zone, so ph's are getting killed....no one can solo Tovax so they all avoid him and let him follow his pathing...lots of quests being initiated in the Qeynos, QHills, Surefall area...etc.,<br>
<br>
There are many 'tricks' in the game that are known by few players...things like getting Hasten to spawn, what ph's are for the AC, and so on. And no one who knows these will just show up on a msg board and post them for the world to see...Knowledge is power, the folks that successfully figure these out are not just going to give it away.<br>
<br>
The best you can hope for on quests like this is about 80% of the information needed...so research it the best you can on boards and such, then do it yourself and try a different approach each time and eventually you may discover it on your own. <br>
